# ctafooter Fields

1. heading (string) - The main heading text
2. description (text) - Brief paragraph for the CTA
3. email (string) - Contact email address
4. phone (string) - Contact phone number
5. address (string) - Physical address
6. ctaLabel (string) - Label for the CTA button
7. ctaLink (url) - Link for the CTA button
8. selectableVariant (string) - The variant (default or xDemo)
9. sortOrder (number) - Placement order among components
10. globalComponentSource (reference) - Optional reference to a global ctafooter